LeadShare.name: LeadShare
LeadShare.description: Represents a sharing entry on a Lead.

IsDeleted.description: Indicates whether the object has been moved to the Recycle Bin (true) or not (false). Label is Deleted.

LeadAccessLevel.description: Level of access that the User or Group has to the Lead. The possible values are: Read Edit All This value is not valid when creating or updating these records.

LeadId.description: ID of the Lead associated with this sharing entry. This field can’t be updated.

RowCause.description: Reason that this sharing entry exists. If you’re creating a sharing entry, the only permitted value is Manual. If no value is specified, the field defaults to Manual. All other RowCause values are read-only. After the sharing entry is created, this field can’t be edited.

UserOrGroupId.description: ID of the User or Group that has been given access to the Lead. This field can’t be updated.
